comments.body:
@taublast  Thank you for confirming that iOS is operational. 
As of right now, `SKGLView` and `SKMetalView` are still not supported on macOS. 
I sure hope this task ([2104](https://github.com/mono/SkiaSharp/issues/2104)) eventually comes to fruition for mac users.  It's a bit dated. Other than this task, I'm unable to find any roadmaps that mention adding GPU support.
